{"tid":1761987,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【抗暴之戰】遭催淚彈擊中頭少年稍好轉對外界有反應 仍留醫ICU暫無生命危險","createTime":"2019-11-29T09:10:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T11:14:20.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3be83caee64893d593fb08a2c0bc881ec00d34a6","tid":1761987,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T09:10:04.000Z","msg":"15歲少年傅同學11月13日晚在天水圍被防暴警發射的催淚彈擊中頭部重創，即晚入院進行開腦手術後持續昏迷，情況未見好轉。事隔兩星期終傳來好消息，協助傅同學的基督教信義會青少年服務總監竺永洪向《蘋果》透露，少年雖然仍在深切治療部留醫，但有輕微好轉，「（清）醒多咗，（傅的）哥哥話細佬有醒過吓，畀到少少反應，但未講到嘢。」據悉，男生暫時沒有生命危險，情況安好。<br />\n<br />\n傅同學父母雙亡，與兄長雙依為命。竺永洪每日跟傅同學的兄長聯絡，有時間便前往探望，據竺所知，傅同學手術後大約一星期後逐步「搣甩」呼吸機，毋須插喉可自己呼吸，惟仍然昏迷；至昨日他再收到好消息，傅的哥哥指弟弟有少許好轉，「有醒過吓，未至於可以講嘢溝通嗰種，但對外界有反應。」<br />\n<br />\n竺永洪透露，傅的哥哥已辭職，全天候照顧弟弟，「keep住同佢互動，希望幫佢快啲醒。」竺沒有跟傅的醫生直接溝通，但引述其兄長指，目前難以確定傅同學能否完全康復至與一般青少年無異、會否有嚴重後遺症等等，無法預料將來是否須面對長期、巨額醫療費用，「第一步都係希望佢盡快好番，（家人）都只可以見步行步。」傅的哥哥目前會接受有心人捐款。<br />\n<br />\n根據現場消息，11月13日晚上約9時，逾百巿民包圍天水圍警署，並在附近街道設路障及磚頭陣，其間向警署投擲汽油彈，警署停車場一度火光熊熊。警方其後在警署高層向外發射催淚彈，短時間內發射至少50枚，未幾防暴警衝出向人群發射催淚彈驅散；至晚上10時許，傅同學在天水圍新北江商場對開，被防暴警發射的催淚彈擊中頭部昏迷，義務救護員進行急救再送院。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191129/60323978\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191129%2F60323978&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLfE18wtZo%2FyF0aYgy6X%2FhPY%3D&h=1cb22153\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191129%2F60323978&h=b506e7e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191129/60323978</a>"},{"pid":"209088e04046ef893225a3d0c4eda1782b663391","tid":1761987,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T09:10:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8083ee2251d7a7adbdb86aa213f71d9d76a34cd1","tid":1761987,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T09:10:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c650471a3aa8ae9c36dca59a9ec578062a643116","tid":1761987,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T09:12:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a977059c25a36e4edf6a3d324956fedc8cfc5a","tid":1761987,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T09:12:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9869c159053d25677c45b8e7082b5201b98e6807","tid":1761987,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T09:15:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a